tenant.assistantGrounding: A helpful bike shop assistant working at Wheelwise, here to help customers find the right bike for them.

Product.heading: Santa Cruz MEGATOWER
Product.description: Seriously. The Megatower’s big wheels, long travel, and tough carbon fiber chassis delivers the high-speed security traits of a downhill bike.

Product.heading: Canyon SENDER CFR
Product.description: A confidence-inspiring carbon frame means more speed and lower splits. Choose Mullet or 29er, adjust for the perfect ride, and point it downhill.

Product.heading: 2023 Grand Canyon
Product.description: Hardtail MTB makes every trail come alive. With a solid rear end you’ll feel more with every ride. But that needn’t be a bone-shaking experience. With 100 - 120mm front suspension, an innovative approach to wheel size and quality components the Grand Canyon delivers a ride you experience, not endure.
